    <title>Meaningless "posted a topic/replied to topic", instead use "question", "discussion", "blog article"</title>
    <updated>2024-11-16T10:39:34.998000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Sandra_Rossi</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/145194</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;I see in my Notification feed questions, discussions and blog posts which are all tagged "posted a new topic" or "replied to topic", and I need to look at the picture to know if it's a question, a blog post or even a discussion. It has taken me months to change my habit from going from the text to the picture, in fact I have to look at both parts, the kind of topic, and the topic title. Why not having the whole information in the text? Proposing to replace "topic" with either&amp;nbsp;"question", "discussion" or "blog article".&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Here, it's a question:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_0-1731749120464.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/191479i6111E67524F4E1D2/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_0-1731749120464.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_0-1731749120464.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;It's a blog post:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_4-1731749739754.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/191483i2FD6AD61B995004B/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_4-1731749739754.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_4-1731749739754.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;It's a discussion:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_3-1731749653050.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/191482i4740E5CA3A58EC3A/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_3-1731749653050.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_3-1731749653050.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Surprisingly, "topic" is not used in "commented on blog article":&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Sandra_Rossi_5-1731749791178.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/191484i771F88E5F8B6CC9C/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Sandra_Rossi_5-1731749791178.png" alt="Sandra_Rossi_5-1731749791178.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thank you.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Sandra&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/questions-about-sap-websites/meaningless-quot-posted-a-topic-replied-to-topic-quot-instead-use-quot/qaq-p/13939578"/>
    <published>2024-11-16T10:39:34.998000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
