    <content>&lt;P class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;I already worked&amp;nbsp;in end-user (accounts payable) full of SAP only. For the past 5 years and 10 months, I have worked&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;at Capgemini and IBM; meanwhile, I have a certificate from IBM learning SAP FICO, and now I want to change my domain. It’s possible. Then if they have 5 years of experience, they will consider it, or they will consider a fresher. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
